iPhone Automation Projects


<Project: Automated Text Forwading>

Problem: 
Important incoming messages needed to be forwarded automatically.

Solution: 
Built an iPhone Siri Shortcut that monitors incoming messages,
checks for keywords, and forwards relevant notifications.


<Project: Wi-Fi Network Logger>

Problem:
Needed a way to be notified and quickly logged when and where the device connected to Wi-Fi networks.

Solution:
Built an automation that runs every time the device connects to a network logging the SSiD, network name, location and timestamp into a Notes document. 
